---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Latest Rumors - CelebScandal Digest" description="Get the scoop on Hollywood's freshest scandals and whispers that are making waves in Tinseltown. From secret affairs to blockbuster betrayals, we've got the dirt!">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B0000] to-[#800020] py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(#ffffff_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:20px_20px]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-block bg-white text-[#8B0000] px-6 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 font-bold tracking-wider">
          <i class="fas fa-fire mr-2"></i> BREAKING NEWS <i class="fas fa-fire ml-2"></i>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
          Latest Rumors
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 mb-8 font-light">
          Hollywood's Hottest Whispers Exposed!
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/20">
          <p class="text-lg text-white">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left mr-2"></i> 
            Get the scoop on Hollywood's freshest scandals and whispers that are making waves in Tinseltown. From secret affairs to blockbuster betrayals, we've got the dirt!
            <i class="fas fa-quote-right ml-2"></i>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Content Section -->
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-12">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#8B0000] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
          <i class="fas fa-gossip text-white text-2xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#8B0000]">Welcome to the Pulse of Scandal</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B0000]/10 to-[#800020]/10 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#8B0000]/30 mb-12">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-4">
          Where the stars' secrets spill faster than a paparazzi flash. At 
          <span class="font-bold text-[#8B0000]">CelebScandal Digest</span>, we're <span class="font-bold underline">unveiling Hollywood's juiciest secrets</span> one rumor at a time.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
          Buckle up for the latest buzz that's got everyone talking!
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Rumor Cards Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-[#8B0000] transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B0000] to-[#800020] relative">
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[#800020] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold">
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i> HOT RUMOR
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Taylor Swift & Travis Kelce</h3>
              <p class="text-sm opacity-90">Mystery Split?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-[#8B0000]">Rumors are swirling</span> that the power couple might be calling it quits after a heated argument at a private LA bash. Insiders claim Swift was overheard saying, 
              <span class="italic">"Football isn't forever, but drama is."</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">
              Could this be the end of #Tayvis? Sources close to the pair hint at reconciliation tours, but we're not holding our breath.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-sm text-[#800020] font-bold">Stay tuned for exclusives!</span>
              <button class="bg-[#8B0000] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#800020] transition-colors">
                <i class="fas fa-newspaper mr-2"></i>Read More
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-[#8B0000] transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4b0026] to-[#8B0000] relative">
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-[#800020] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold">
              <i class="fas fa-fire"></i> BREAKING
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Brad Pitt</h3>
              <p class="text-sm opacity-90">Secret Rendezvous</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-[#8B0000]">Fresh off his F1</span> saga, Brad Pitt is allegedly meeting with a rising starlet at exclusive beachside venues. 
              <span class="italic">"The chemistry is electric,"</span> insiders say.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium">
              Details are emerging about this secretive liaison that could shake Hollywood to its core.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-sm text-[#800020] font-bold">No official word yet</span>
              <button class="bg-[#8B0000] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#800020] transition-colors">
                <i class="fas fa-newspaper mr-2"></i>Read More
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Section -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#800020] to-[#8B0000] rounded-3xl p-8 mb-16 text-white">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <div class="md:w-1/3 mb-6 md:mb-0 flex justify-center">
            <div class="bg-white/20 p-6 rounded-full">
              <i class="fas fa-gavel text-5xl"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3 md:pl-8">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Unleash the Truth</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-4">
              Our investigative team works around the clock to bring you the unfiltered truth behind Hollywood's biggest scandals. 
              We dig deeper than the headlines, uncovering the stories that shape entertainment culture.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="bg-white text-[#8B0000] px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold mr-4">
                <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> 24/7 Scandal Coverage
              </div>
              <div class="bg-white/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold">
                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Anonymous Sources
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="text-center py-12">
        <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#8B0000] mb-6">Never Miss a Scandal Again</h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Subscribe to our breaking news alerts and stay ahead of the gossip curve.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" class="px-6 py-4 rounded-full border-2 border-[#8B0000] focus:outline-none focus:border-[#800020] text-lg w-full sm:w-80">
          <button class="bg-[#8B0000] hover:bg-[#800020] text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg transition-colors">
            <i class="fas fa-bell mr-2"></i> Get Alerts
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer CTA -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B0000] to-[#800020] py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Join the Scandal Revolution</h3>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Become part of the most exclusive gossip circle in Hollywood
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <button class="bg-white text-[#8B0000] hover:bg-[#800020] hover:text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg transition-colors">
          <i class="fas fa-user-plus mr-2"></i> Sign Up Now
        </button>
        <button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#8B0000] font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg transition-colors">
          <i class="fas fa-newspaper mr-2"></i> Browse Archives
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>